target.message:
Close branch. Default branch is now where the gtk version lives, until
the Qt port is stable, when it will be merged in, replacing the gtk version there.

The sole change I made in this branch didn't work anyway, as we were actually
using features from gtk 2.24, and I would had to have made additional changes
in order to be compatible with 2.22.
Update to match new labscript design where builtins are also cleaned-up by labscript as well as runmanager.

When making a shot file, create all parent directories if they don't exist,
and do not error if they do already exist.

Merged in open-all (pull request #43)

Open all groups of selected globals files.
Fix bug with underscores to the right of the decimal point.
